title: Ep. - 531 - JOE AMABILE FROM THE BACHELORETTE AND BACHELOR IN PARADISE REVIEW OF SELLING THE OC
description:
Joe Amabile from The Bachelorette and Bachelor in Paradise discusses the anxiety he experienced during filming, how the experience of being on both shows helped him overcome it, and his engagement to Serena Pitt.

 

Producer Chris DeRosa helps Kate review Selling the OC on Netflix.
